rows.label: qst201101_0010
rows.name: Nia, stop!

rows.label: qst201101_0020
rows.name: What's up?

rows.label: qst201101_0030
rows.name: A lance?!

rows.label: qst201101_0040
rows.name: Enemies?!

rows.label: qst201101_0050
rows.name: What direction did it come from?

rows.label: qst201101_0060
rows.name: I don't know.

rows.label: qst201101_0070
rows.name: But I think we'll be fine now.

rows.label: qst201101_0080
rows.name:
Whoever threw the lance seems
to have run off somewhere.

rows.label: qst201101_0090
rows.name: Why'd they throw a lance at us, though?

rows.label: qst201101_0100
rows.name: Maybe they were trying to pick you off?

rows.label: qst201101_0110
rows.name:
Why would they wanna off me? Anyone else
here would make more sense.

rows.label: qst201101_0120
rows.name:
They probably just fudged their aim and it
ended up heading your way.

rows.label: qst201101_0130
rows.name: Ugh, this is the worst.

rows.label: qst201101_0140
rows.name:
No, if someone wanted us dead, they wouldn't be using
such an unreliable method.

rows.label: qst201101_0150
rows.name: So can we take that as a warning or something?

rows.label: qst201101_0170
rows.name: Well, I think it's going to be more like 'back off'.

rows.label: qst201101_0180
rows.name: Hmm... It's hard to tell.

rows.label: qst201101_0190
rows.name:
Anyway, there's one thing that's clear:
someone has their eye on us.

rows.label: qst201101_0200
rows.name: Just keep on the lookout, OK?

rows.label: qst201101_0210
rows.name: Hold on. There's something attached to it.

rows.label: qst201101_0220
rows.name: You're right! Let's have a look then.
